Concierge Services
As a valued Premier customer, we recognize that your time is valuable and you need easy access to services that can help simplify your busy life.  With  Premier World MasterCard¬Æ Concierge Services1, let us make your dinner reservations, purchase tickets to events, coordinate business arrangements worldwide, locate hard-to-find items, buy and deliver gifts and much more. For convenience, the cost of goods or services can be billed to your Premier World MasterCard¬Æ.  To learn more, speak to an HSBC Premier Concierge representative any time, any day, by calling 888.314.5132.

1 The World MasterCard¬Æ Concierge Service is administered by VIPdesk. Certain restrictions, limitations and exclusions may apply. This service is administered by a company not affiliated with HSBC Bank USA, N.A.
