 HSBC Holdings plc (HSBC), launched on January 1, 1959, is the banking and financial services company. The Company manages its products and services through four business areas: Retail Banking and Wealth Management (RBWM), Commercial Banking (CMB), Global Banking and Markets (GB&M), and Global Private Banking (GPB). The Company operates across various geographical regions, which include Europe, Asia, Middle East and North Africa, North America and Latin America. As of December 31, 2016, the Company operated in 70 countries and territories across the world..
