HSBC - Wikipedia





















 






HSBC

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

This article is about the HSBC Group. For the Hong Kong bank, see The Hongkong and Shanghai Banking Corporation.

HSBC Holdings PLC





Type

Public limited company


